Text: Now all I have to do is wait for wetmouse to say something stupid.
You know what they say: Those that can't do teach. And those that can't even manage that most simple of tasks spend all their days posting right-wing propaganda to torrent sites. What a life!
And there it is! Ah, the irony of being called pitiful by a thing that sits around creating new screen names for itself all day. Shouldn't you be out uselessly occupying something?
